President Barack Obama signs an executive order placing sanctions and visa bans on people that contributed to the current crisis in Crimea. (CNN)An Israeli helicopter strike near the border with Syria kills two senior IRGC figures and six members of Hezbollah. (Reuters), (Xinhua)Paramount Pictures orders theater chains, including those in Cleveland, Atlanta, and New Orleans, not to re-release the 2004 film Team America: World Police, which depicts a fictional mission to kill Kim Jong-il. (Mercury News)(The Times-Picayune)